"@PostMapping("/{id}/reviews")
public Review saveReview(@PathVariable int id, @RequestBody Review review) {
review.setProduct(ps.finfById(id));
return rr.saveReview(review);
} What is @RequestBo here? "

@RequestBody is is used to accept a request from the client
@RequestBody is used to send response back to client
@RequestBody is used to Generate json response
@RequestBody is used to accept request object body from the client
